            <title>[SOLR-2225] CoreContainer#register should use checkDefault to normalize the core name</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/SOLR-2225</link>
                <project id="12310230" key="SOLR">Solr</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;fail case:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;start with default collection set to collection1&lt;br/&gt;
remove core collection1&lt;br/&gt;
default collection on CoreContainer is still set to collection1&lt;br/&gt;
add core collection1&lt;br/&gt;
it doesn&apos;t act like the default core&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;we might do as the summary suggests, or when the default core is removed, we reset to no default core until one is again explicitly set&lt;/p&gt;</description>
